---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Class 12th English — Study Material, Notes & Q&A"
description: "Browse all study materials, question answers, and notes for Bihar Board Class 12th English (Rainbow)."
permalink: /class-12/
breadcrumbs:
  - { label: "Home", url: "/" }
  - { label: "Class 12th" }
---

<div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem;">
  <header style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">🎓 Class 12th English</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
      Complete study materials, line-by-line Hindi meaning, and question answers for Bihar Board Class 12th (Rainbow).
    </p>
  </header>

  <div style="display: grid; gap: 1.5rem;">
    {% set count = 0 %}
    {% for post in collections['class-12'] %}
      {% set count = count + 1 %}
      <article style="background: var(--bg-raised); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.5rem; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.4;">
          <a href="{{ post.url }}" style="color: var(--text-primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700;">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
        </h2>
        {% if post.data.description %}
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" style="display: inline-block; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem;">Read More →</a>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
    
    {% if count == 0 %}
      <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-secondary); padding: 3rem; background: var(--bg-raised); border-radius: var(--radius-md);">More articles coming soon!</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>
